  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advocating for pro-poor social protection in the UK</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Continuing to work with the Welfare Reform Consortium to push for amendments to the Welfare Reform Bill that mitigate its negative impact on people living in poverty, and particularly on gender equality. Developing and maintaining an ongoing relationship with the Consortium and contributing to the development of ongoing work and cooperation through the Consortium.    Commissioning work to demonstrate the extent of corporate welfare in the UK, and using that research to challenge the negative portrayal of the welfare system and of benefit claimants.</narrative>
  </description>
